
Steve Stombler is a Davis resident and landscape architect.  He built the Clepsydra in E Street Plaza (however, he is not the artist who designed it).  He has also built the straw bale walls near the Davis Waldorf School.  To see some other straw bale construction in Davis, check out Straw Bale Bench.

